---
title: Spanish Style Halloumi with Bulgur and Flaked Almonds
description: The marinade on this halloumi is something of a taste sensation. Sharp red wine vinegar, smoked paprika and sweet honey are balanced perfectly with the saltiness from the halloumi. And Chef Andre’s talents don’t stop there - nutty bulgur, crunchy flaked almonds and peppery rocket are the dream accompaniment to this deliciously nutritious weeknight dinner. We’ll pass your compliments to the Chef!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spanish-style-halloumi-wk42-d5066b95.jpg
